name: The Strongest Assassin of the Zoldyck Family!
summary: Upon traversing into the world of Hunter, Ron becomes a member of the Zoldyck family and awakens a unique type of nen ability.By gathering specific traits, he can create corresponding nen beasts.Gathering traits from the Zoldyck Estate creates the nen beast "Killer Queen."Gathering traits from the Hunter Exam creates the nen beast "Gourmet Hunter, Toriko."Gathering traits from the Heavens Arena creates the nen beast "Top Fighting Creature, Baki Hanma."Gathering traits from Meteor City creates the nen beast "Cyber Girl, Chii."-----------------Disclaimer: All rights to the original content belong to their respective creators.Author:Book:  'Translator: Idkjust
